headline:"Calm Studios scales the Calmlings wellness universe with Gemini API",wr:"Calm Studios integrates Nano Banana and Veo models to develop wellness-minded entertainment, amassing over 1.5 billion video views and 4 million social media followers in less than six months.",Ce:[{name:"Jesper Gustavsson",role:"VP, Product Management"},{name:"Anastasia Avramenko",role:"Head of Marketing & Growth"},{name:"Christopher Scoville",role:"Consultant"},{name:"Sean Webster",role:"Consultant"}],thumbnail:{src:"https://www.gstatic.com/aistudio/case_studies/calm_studios/calmstudios_thumbnail.png",
type:"image",alt:"Calm Studios showcase hero"}}},{type:"cta",content:{link:"https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/new_chat?model=gemini-3-pro-image"}},{type:"text",content:{body:'\n            <p>\n              \u201cWe founded Calm Studios to make the world happier and healthier through human-led, AI-accelerated entertainment. Tied to the ethos of the Calm app, our entertainment company complements sleep, meditation, and relaxation activities with Calmlings \u2014 delightful characters designed to help users build healthy habits,\u201d say co-founders Michael Acton-Smith and Alex Tew.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              To realize the vision of blending mindfulness with high-quality multimedia content, <a href="https://calmstudios.com/">Calm Studios</a> needed to scale their creative output. By integrating Gemini and Veo models into their production pipeline, the team accelerates video development and unlocks new product offerings to reach millions of users around the world.\n            </p>'}},
{type:"video",content:{video:{sources:[{url:"https://www.gstatic.com/aistudio/case_studies/calm_studios/calmstudios_calmlings-veo.mp4",type:"video/mp4"}]}}},{type:"text",content:{header:{headline:"<h2>Bringing characters to life with Nano Banana and Veo</h2>"},body:'\n            <p>\n              Calm Studios integrates <a href="https://aistudio.google.com/models/gemini-3-pro-image">Nano Banana</a> to develop the visual foundations for the Calmlings universe, conceptualizing both the central characters and the immersive environments they inhabit. They also use the model to prototype physical products, such as character plushes, enabling the team to envision the Calmlings in entirely new ways.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              The team uses <a href="https://aistudio.google.com/models/veo-3">Veo</a> to seamlessly translate the static concepts developed through Nano Banana into engaging, emotionally resonant audiovisual content with high fidelity. Veo helps characters lead breathing exercises, recite affirmations, and spread positivity to a wellness-minded audience. Within a five-month period, these videos have amassed over 1 billion views and reached millions of followers across TikTok, YouTube, Instagram, and Facebook.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              Building on the success of their short-form video assets, the team is building an interactive gaming experience designed to practice self-care by taking care of Calmlings, with long-term aspirations of expanding this wellness universe into a full-length feature film.\n            </p>'}},
{type:"images",content:{items:[{image:{src:"https://www.gstatic.com/aistudio/case_studies/calm_studios/calmstudios_calmlings-socialfeed.png",alt:"Calmlings receive millions of views on Instagram"}}]}},{type:"quote",content:{quote:"We\u2019ve used Nano Banana and Veo to produce over 500 videos for our social media accounts. We see these models as a pillar of our Calmlings wellness universe and a key part of our product roadmap.",author:"- Anastasia Avramenko, Head of Marketing & Growth at Calm Studios"}},
{type:"text",content:{header:{headline:"<h2>Harmonizing qualitative and quantitative analysis with Gemini 3 Pro</h2>"},body:"\n            <p>\n              To sustain their rapid growth and consistently engage their audience, Calm Studios developed an AI agent system powered by Gemini 3 Pro to aid in their overarching social media strategy.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              The team\u2019s multi-agent framework uses the model to analyze social media posts by processing raw video inputs alongside text descriptions and transcripts, then combining this qualitative data with quantitative performance metrics. This pipeline enables the agents to identify themes, brainstorm new content ideas, and create storyboards. The system can then pass these concepts back to Nano Banana and Veo to generate visuals.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              Beyond content strategy, they cite Gemini 3 Pro\u2019s Deep Research and Search capabilities to perform complex market analysis and technical deep-dives.\n            </p>"}},
{type:"text",content:{header:{headline:"<h2>The future of mindful entertainment</h2>"},body:"\n            <p>\n              Calm Studios is uniquely positioned to deliver mindful entertainment for a global audience. By integrating generative AI models for everything from high-quality asset creation to strategic planning, the studio demonstrates how a playful and purposeful approach to wellness can effectively scale to millions of users worldwide.\n            </p>"}},{type:"text",content:{body:'\n            <p>\n              To get started with the Gemini API, read the <a href="https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api">developer documentation</a>.\n            </p>'}},
