modules:[{type:"hero",content:{date:"February 18, 2026",headline:"Wolffun Game Studio accelerates PvP game development with Gemini 2.5 Flash Image and 2.5 Pro",wr:"By integrating Gemini API models and tools into development workflows, Wolffun automates engineering tasks, optimizes game logic, and enhances creative production for award-winning games like Thetan Immortal.",Ce:[{name:"Nguyen Dinh Khanh",role:"CEO, Wolffun Game"}],thumbnail:{src:"",type:"image",alt:"Wolffun Game showcase hero"}}},{type:"stats",
content:{stats:[{value:"90%",description:"Reduction in code review time for senior engineers"},{value:"40%",description:"Increase in creative asset production"}]}},{type:"cta",content:{link:"https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/new_chat?model=gemini-pro-latest"}},{type:"text",content:{body:'\n            <p>\n              Founded in 2014, <a href="https://www.wolffungame.com/">Wolffun Game Studio</a> has established itself as a pioneer in mobile online PvP games. From early hits like the blockchain phenomenon Thetan Arena, which garnered over 30 million players, to its latest 1 v. 1 archery combat game, Thetan Immortal, Wolffun pushes the boundaries of competitive gaming for a global audience.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              Wolffun chose Gemini API for its versatile model family, using Gemini 2.5 Pro and 2.5 Flash Image to help accelerate development cycles by reducing code review time and boosting creative output.\n            </p>'}},
{type:"youtube_video",content:{video:{YG:"JXlkyFrGn4g",legend:"Thetan Immortal won Google Play\u2019s 2025 \u2018Best Made in Vietnam\u2019 Award."}}},{type:"text",content:{header:{headline:"<h2>From game logic to dialogue: Building experiences with Gemini 2.5 Pro</h2>"},body:"\n            <p>\n              Game development is an intricate dance between rapid iteration, technical complexity, and creative excellence. Traditional bottlenecks \u2013 from time-consuming code reviews and exhaustive technical research to repetitive content generation \u2013 can slow down progress and divert valuable developer time away from innovation.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              The Wolffun team leverages advanced, long context reasoning in Gemini 2.5 Pro for:\n            </p>\n            <ul>\n              <li>\n                <b>Source code analysis:</b> The team built an automated GitHub bot that analyzes entire codebases to suggest shader optimizations and refactor legacy systems\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <b>Game design & balancing:</b> The model creates complex documentation and balancing formulas, analyzing historical player match data to calculate bot difficulty curves, and generating concepts for game mechanics\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <b>Engineering tasks:</b> The model automates high-level engineering tasks and debugs existing code, going beyond simple code completion\n              </li>\n              <li>\n                <b>Story development and localization:</b> The model generates rich backstories and dialogues in 8 languages, tracking cultural nuances so they are more accurately conveyed.\n              </li>\n            </ul>"}},
{type:"images",content:{items:[{image:{src:"https://www.gstatic.com/aistudio/case_studies/wolffun/wolffun-inline-small.jpg",alt:"The Wolffun team uses proprietary tools, including a metadata tool and automated GitHub bot, that integrate Gemini models."},legend:"The Wolffun team uses proprietary tools, including a metadata tool and automated GitHub bot, that integrate Gemini models."}]}},{type:"text",content:{body:"\n            <p>\n              The automated review tools have helped to reduce code review time by 50% for junior developers and up to 90% for senior developers, allowing lead engineers to focus on architecture and innovation. Complex tasks like calculating difficulty scaling formulas, which previously took days of manual calculation, are now handled in minutes by 2.5 Pro.\n            </p>"}},
{type:"quote",content:{quote:"The performance of Gemini 2.5 Pro in tasks requiring complex reasoning, coding, and problem-solving demonstrated a clear advantage. For a game studio, the ability to efficiently handle tasks like performance optimization and complex game logic generation is a decisive advantage.",author:"\u2014 Nguyen Dinh Khanh, CEO of Wolffun Game"}},{type:"text",content:{header:{headline:"<h2>Generating concept art Gemini 2.5 Flash Image</h2>"},body:"\n            <p>\n              Beyond code, Wolffun uses Gemini 2.5 Flash Image for rapid visual brainstorming and asset creation. The team noted that integrating the model boosted efficiency by 40% and banner production by 35-40%, accelerating time-to-market for marketing campaigns.\n            </p>"}},
{type:"images",content:{items:[{image:{src:"https://www.gstatic.com/aistudio/case_studies/wolffun/wolffun-demo.gif",alt:"Gemini 2.5 Flash Image generates new character art from a reference image."},legend:"Gemini 2.5 Flash Image generates new character art from a reference image."}]}},{type:"text",content:{body:"\n            <p>\n              The team appreciated that \u201cthe availability of models like Gemini 2.5 Flash and 2.5 Flash-Lite gives us the flexibility to choose the right balance of performance and cost for high-volume tasks like player support, making our AI integration financially sustainable.\u201d\n            </p>"}},
{type:"text",content:{header:{headline:"<h2>Powering the next generation of personalized gaming</h2>"},body:"\n            <p>\n              Looking ahead, Wolffun views Gemini models as a foundational technology for hyper-personalized gaming experiences. They also plan to build AI-generated content pipelines to create real-time, personalized quests or in-game events based on a player\u2019s recent actions, delivering a unique game world to the individual.\n            </p>\n            <p>\n              Wolffun\u2019s success underscores the immense potential for AI to help revolutionize game development, empowering teams to build faster, innovate more freely, and ultimately deliver more engaging experiences to players worldwide.\n            </p>"}},
